---
import "../styles/global.css";
import MarkdownPostLayout from "../layouts/MarkdownPostLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Design Page";
---

<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>Lublio H1</h1>
      <h2>Lublio H2</h2>
      <h3>Lublio H3</h3>
      <h1 class="kor">루블리오 H1</h1>
      <h2 class="kor">루블리오 H2</h2>
      <h3 class="kor">루블리오 H3</h3>

      <p>
        Lublio isn't just about learning a language; it's about embracing the
        freedom to explore the world with confidence. Our app is tailored for
        the modern wanderer, offering: French, German, and any other European
        languages.
      </p>

      <p class="kor">
        루블리오는 단순히 언어를 배우는 것이 아닙니다. 자신감 있게 세상을 탐험할
        자유를 누리는 것입니다. 현대적인 방랑자를 위해 맞춤 제작된 저희 앱은
        프랑스어, 독일어 및 기타 유럽 언어들을 제공합니다.
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top: 60px;">
        <h2>Text Box</h2>

        <div class="text-box">
          <p>
            Lublio isn't just about learning a language; it's about embracing
            the freedom to explore the world with confidence. Our app is
            tailored for the modern wanderer, offering:
          </p>
          <ul class="styled-list">
            <li>
              Quick, practical lessons focused on real-world travel scenarios
            </li>
            <li>Cultural insights that help you blend in and avoid faux pas</li>
            <li>
              Location-based content that adapts to your travel destination
            </li>
            <li>Offline mode for learning on-the-go, even in remote areas</li>
            <li>Interactive challenges that make learning fun and addictive</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 60px;">
        <h2>Buttons</h2>
        <ul style={{ listStyle: "none" }}>
          <button>
            Welche Art von Visum benötige ich für die Einreise ins Land?
          </button>
          <button>Какой тип визы мне нужен для въезда в страну?</button>
          <button>
            Quel type de visa ai-je besoin pour entrer dans le pays?
          </button>
          <button>What type of visa do I need to enter the country?</button>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
